# non-authoritative repo dotenv example.
#
# Do not copy this file for normal Swarm setup. Production and user-facing
# Swarm commands do not auto-load repo `.env` files.
#
# Use swarm.example.yaml as the non-secret swarm.yaml reference, and use
# `swarm secrets set` / `swarm secrets check` for credentials required by
# contracts. Do not place durable Swarm setup in repo `.env` files.
#
# Direct shell environment variables are a narrow bootstrap/compatibility
# surface. Use them only where an owning spec section explicitly names them,
# and keep assignments out of repo `.env` files.
